EU Says Recapitalization of European Banks Is Ongoing

-- B y   J o n e s   H a y d e n
-- 
2011-09-23T10:24:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/eu-says-recapitalization-of-european-banks-is-ongoing.html
The recapitalization of European
banks is ongoing, the European Union said.  “Since 2008, the amount of the recapitalization of
European banks is more than 420 billion” euros, Olivier Bailly,
a spokesman for the European Commission, told reporters in
Brussels today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
